Package edu.uiuc.ncsa.qdl.expressions

Class StemExtractionNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uiuc.ncsa.qdl.expressions.ExpressionImpl
      • edu.uiuc.ncsa.qdl.expressions.StemExtractionNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExpressionNode, ExpressionInterface, HasResultInterface, Statement, Serializable
    public class StemExtractionNode
extends ExpressionImpl
    This will allow for creating a subset (copy of portion) of a stem. The result is a stem completely indep. of the original.
